snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Backlogged - Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Ohhh man! After a long and arduous 1.5 years, the FULL version of FNaF Backlogged is finally ready for release! As of this point forward, the game is completely finished! It's been such a wonderful journey getting here - thank you all for your support, it truly means the world! 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/OkieDokiiii
GameJolt page: https://gamejolt.com/games/FNaFBacklogged/799414

Music Used:
Planet Obliterator 5000 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a0pq0M7FfCM

Five Nights at Freddy's: Backlogged is an arcade-style bullet heaven game set in the Five Nights at Freddy's universe. Destroy waves of enemies, upgrade your stats, and ultimately conquer each round in this high-action new take on the Five Nights at Freddy's series! But be warned - it seems that something isn't quite right...

Enjoy :D
